PrecisRegulations Amending the BOATING RESTRICTION REGULATIONS by imposing area- specific speed limits, by prohibiting persons under 12 from operating personal watercraft, by changing the term "peace officer" to "enforcement officer" throughout the Regulations and by correcting discrepancies between the English and French versions.

precis:
Regulations Amending the BOATING RESTRICTION REGULATIONS by imposing area-
specific speed limits, by prohibiting persons under 12 from operating
personal watercraft, by changing the term "peace officer" to "enforcement
officer" throughout the Regulations and by correcting discrepancies between
the English and French versions.
